                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq3">
                                How can I schedule a property visit?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
                        <div id="faq3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                            <div class="accordion-body">
                                You can book a property visit directly through our website. Just click "Book a Visit" on any property listing, choose your preferred date and time, and we'll confirm your appointment.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="accordion-item mb-3 border-0 shadow-sm">
                        <h2 class="accordion-header">
                            <button class="accordion-button collapsed fw-bold" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faq4">
                                Do you provide home loan assistance?
                            </button>
                        </h2>
